data.description: Cozy 4 sides brick, 3 bed/2bath, 1 story home. New roof 2017. New appliances. Ceramic tile, ceiling fans, garden tub, separate shower, window blinds, walk in closets, over the range microwave, and security alarm system. Low maintenance landscaping. Quiet street in established neighborhood. Located near schools, shopping, major highways, Lackland AFB, Sea World and Fiesta Texas. Why rent when you can own for even less!
